#Welcome to the support page for Playlist+!
##My name is Ian Burns and I created Playlists+
##If you have any: ###* Questions ###* Issues ###* Recommendations ###* Comments ##I'm happy to hear them. Just send me an email at ianb821@gmail.com and I'll get back to you as soon as possible. Thanks for using the app, I hope you enjoy it!
